PrecisAmendments to the IMMIGRATION REGULATIONS, 1978 adding the Republic of Korea to the list of countries whose citizens do not require visitor visas and removing transit visas requirement for passengers travelling on flights to or from the United States which stop in Canada to refuel provided the person is in possession of a valid U.S. visa.
